41 located in Indiana, but before the virtual currency kiosk allows the
42 user to initiate a virtual currency transaction through the virtual
HB 1116—LS 6503/DI 119

17
1 currency kiosk, the operator of the virtual currency kiosk shall
2 provide the user with the following information on the electronic
