38 Sec. 19. (a) Before accepting payment from a user through a
39 virtual currency kiosk that is located in Indiana, the operator of
40 the virtual currency kiosk shall:
41 (1) verify the identity of the user by:
42 (A) requiring the user to submit to the operator a copy of
HB 1116—LS 6503/DI 119

19
1 a government issued identification card that identifies the
2 user; or
3 (B) obtaining verification of the identity of the user
4 through an agent of the operator that requires the user to
5 submit to the agent a copy of a government issued
6 identification card that identifies the user; and
7 (2) require the user to submit to the operator the user's name,
