10 subdivision must match the information on the government
11 issued identification card described in subdivision (1).
12 (b) The operator of a virtual currency kiosk that is located in
13 Indiana may not allow a user to engage in a virtual currency
14 transaction through the virtual currency kiosk under a name or
15 identity that is not verified as the user's name and identity under
16 subsection (a).
